videos.description: Troy's Brandon Silvers' pass is incomplete due to Arkansas State's Dee Liner, who swats the ball.
videos.headline: Batted pass forces a Troy punt

videos.description: Justice Hansen's pass is intercepted by Blace Brown, who gets injured on the play and leaves the game.
videos.headline: Troy's Brown intercepts pass in red zone

videos.description: Marcus Jones returns the ball 99 yards after the kickoff for a Troy touchdown.
videos.headline: Troy takes kickoff return to the house

videos.description: Justice Hansen finds the hole and runs for a Red Wolves touchdown.
videos.headline: Arkansas' QB runs in for TD

videos.description: Troy head coach Neal Brown says the team needs to get plays going in the second half.
videos.headline: Coach says Troy needs to loosen up

videos.description: Justice Hansen finds Blake Mack who makes a great leaping catch with a defender on his tail.
videos.headline: Great catch by Red Wolves' Mack

videos.description: Trojans' Brandon Silvers launches the ball to Tray Eafford for a 44-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Troy capitalizes off penalty with TD

videos.description: Arkansas State's Justice Hansen finds Blake Mack who dodges multiple tackles across the field for 31-yards.
videos.headline: Red Wolves' Mack zig zags across field to red zone

videos.description: Red Wolves kicker Sawyer Williams completely misses a 36-yard field-goal attempt.
videos.headline: Arkansas State shanks 36-yard FG

videos.description: Josh Anderson receives a pass and fumbles and the Red Wolves' Michael Johnson recovers.
videos.headline: Troy fumbles, putting Arkansas in scoring position

videos.description: Arkansas State's Justice Hansen's pass is intercepted in the end zone by Troy's Marcus Jones who takes it to the house.
videos.headline: Troy's Jones takes it to the house with pick-6

videos.description: Red Wolves QB Justice Hansen throws another interception, this time caught by Trojans' Tyler Murray.
videos.headline: Arkansas State's Hansen throws back-to-back picks

videos.description: Johnston White runs up the seam for 33 yards and an Arkansas State first down.
videos.headline: Trojans' White zig-zags for 33 yards

videos.description: Trojans QB Justice Hansen finds Omar Bayless in the end zone, who makes a great leaping catch.
videos.headline: Arkansas State closes the gap with TD

videos.description: Arkansas State QB Justice Hansen launches the ball to Christian Booker for a 39-yard touchdown but the ensuing two-point conversion failed.
videos.headline: Trojans take the lead by 1 with TD

videos.description: Brandon Silvers finds Deondre Douglas for a Trojans touchdown. Later, they complete a trick play for a two-point conversion.
videos.headline: Troy's last-second TD wins game

videos.description: Sun Belt commissioner Karl Benson presents Troy with the championship trophy.
videos.headline: Troy celebrates Sun Belt Championship

videos.description: Troy head coach Neal Brown shares what this victory means to him, and how Marcus Jones and his QB performed.
videos.headline: Coach Brown elated over Troy's victory

videos.description: Trojans QB Brandon Silvers breaks down how this game was different from last year's game, and what this victory means to him as a senior.
videos.headline: Troy QB Silvers explains what went different this year

videos.description: Troys' Marcus Jones breaks down his two non-offensive touchdowns, and what it means to him to contribute to this championship victory.
videos.headline: Trojans' Jones plays huge role in win
